Cryptogram Solver
by Miriam Barnum
   Christina Teodorescu
   Sam Pottash
   Sierra Katow

Instructions:
1) Download all files in /code directory.
2) Download the python nltk library: http://nltk.org/install.html
3) In your terminal, go inside the directory in which you have saved the /code files.
4) Run make.
5) Run ./Cryptogramsolver "YOUR CRYPTOGRAM HERE"
6) Run python nlp.py
    ** You may get an error saying that a certain file is missing that is used to create the part of speech tree. If this is the case, simply follow the directions it gives you and install the missing file.
7) Be amazed!!!
